    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical choice for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. Mechanically, it remains solid; the engine starts reliably and the car handles safely on the road. However, it does show its age with some visible wear and tear, including minor dents on the exterior and some fading in the upholstery. While it isn't a showpiece, it is a functional and honest vehicle that has been regularly serviced to ensure it stays roadworthy. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a budget-friendly option that still has plenty of life left in it.",
      "price": 19500.0,
