    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, having been preserved to rigorous showroom standards with exhaustive attention to detail. Every element, from the pristine interior upholstery to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a legacy of meticulous ownership and climate-controlled storage. For the discerning driver who demands absolute aesthetic and mechanical integrity, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly distinguished asset. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
