      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, appearing as though it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Every body panel is original with perfectly uniform gaps. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and taut with no visible wear on the seat bolsters, steering wheel, or touchpoints, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of service records included to verify its history. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure or corrosion. This is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise. Sale includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and the original window sticker.",
      "price": 48500.0,
